在世界范围内，街机面临衰退<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gcores.com/articles/19617|title=从经营者角度谈谈游戏厅没落的原因|date=2016-07-10|accessdate=2018-12-04|language=zh-hans|website=[[机核|机核]]|author=davchen|archive-date=2018-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181204195108/https://www.gcores.com/articles/19617|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gcores.com/articles/23692|title=街机厅老板：为什么把游戏撤了|date=2017-03-26|accessdate=2018-12-04|language=zh-hans|website=[[机核|机核]]|author=davchen|archive-date=2018-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181204195148/https://www.gcores.com/articles/23692|dead-url=no}}</ref>，中国大陆也不例外。

